ION3 BINDINGS

`Mod1' is the left ALT key and `Mod4' any WINDOWS key.

   Mod4+S: split frame vertically
   Mod4+D: split frame horizontally
   Mod4+F: resize or move frame, then:
       <arrow>: grow in specified direction
       Mod4+<arrow>: shrink in specified direction
       Mod4+Shift+<arrow>: move in specified direction
   Mod4+G: close object
   Mod4+H: unsplit frames
   Mod4+J: create new workspace
   Mod4+K: kill window

   Mod4+E: detach window or reattach it to its previous location
   Mod4+R: attach window to frame
   Mod4+T: toggle tag for this window
   Mod4+Y: tile frame if no tiling exists
   Mod4+U: clear all tags

   Mod1+Space: scratchpad
   Mod4+[12345]: go to specified workspace
   Mod4+Return: fullscreen
   Mod4+<arrow>: go to next frame in this direction
   Mod4+Shift+<arrow>: go to next screen in this direction
   Mod4+Tab: next tab
   Mod4+Shift+Tab: previous tab
   Mod4+Escape: exit ion3
   Mod4+Shift+Escape: restart ion3

   Mod4+F1: display this help
   Mod4+F2: web browser ($BROWSER)
   Mod4+F3: terminal emulator ($TERM)
   Mod4+L: lock screen using xlock
   Mod4+PrtScr: take a screenshot using scrot
